Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text:
The Property is situated along Nassim Road, the prime and exclusive residential district that are occupied by affluent locals, expatriates, foreign communities and the nouveau riche. Dubbed the “crème de la crème” of Singapore’s residential address, Nassim Road is also known as the embassy row due to the numerous numbers of embassies setting there. The Embassy of Japan, Embassy of The Republic of Philippines and the Embassy of the Russian Federation are all located along Nassim Road. Besides a few low-rise bespoke and luxurious private residential developments, such as Nassim Park Residences, Nassim Jade and Nassim Lodge, that are located nearer to Tanglin Road at the south-east end of Nassim Road, the entire stretch of Nassim Road comprises detached houses on sprawling grounds. 

Nestled amongst the luscious quiet green landscapes, the Property is approximately 500m to the verdant Singapore Botanic Gardens – Singapore’s first and only UNESCO Heritage Site. The Orchard Road shopping belt, which is the finest shopping and lifestyle destination in prominent commercial landmarks such as ION Orchard, Wheelock Place, Paragon and Ngee Ann City, is about 2km away from the Property. 

The Property enjoys unparalleled connectivity as it is well-served by major arterial roads and is connected to the rest of the island via the Central Expressway (CTE). Public transportation is easily available along Tanglin Road. The Central Business District is a short 10-minute drive away.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
The Property comprises a 2-storey conservation detached house sited on 3 land plots which together form a regular and elevated land configuration that is excellent for maximizing design efficiency. The combined plots come with a frontage of approximately 70 metres along Nassim Road.

The lower storey has a covered driveway, a garage for 7 cars, a pump room, a switch room, a water tank room and a passageway leading to a private lift.

The upper storey has a swimming pool, an entrance hall, a living room, a dining room, a master bedroom with ensuite bathroom, a guest room with ensuite bathroom, 2 other bedrooms with loft and ensuite bathrooms, internal landscaped courtyard with pond, a kitchen, a laundry area and a helper’s room.
